Monitis,is,a,monitoring,service,meant,to,simplify,the,tracking,of,all,of,your,online,operations,from,web,traffic,and,server,loads,to,server,and,network,monitoring,The,Monitis,Open,API,allows,for,the,extension,and,customization,of,their,existing,platform,Developers,can,access,and,update,contact,information,layouts,notifications,and,monitors,Developers,can,also,access,user,information,including,sub,accounts,The,RESTful,API,provides,data,as,JSON,default,or,XML